title: Salisbury's Caylin Meikrantz is lehighvalleylive Girls Soccer Player of Week
text:
By Josh Folck | For lehighvalleylive.com on October 07, 2015 10:30 AM, updated October 07, 2015 11:43 AM 
GIRLS SOCCER PLAYER OF THE WEEK Caylin Meikrantz (lehighvalleylive file photo ) 
The Falcons junior tallied seven assists in the team's 9-1 win over Palmerton on Tuesday. 
The big night allowed Meikrantz to become the program's all-time leader in assists. 
On Saturday, she scored the game's only goal in a 1-0 road win over Pleasant Valley. 
HONORABLE MENTION: Sr. D Kylie Paul , Saucon Valley; Sr. M Annika Sundlof , Saucon Valley; GK April Foley , Central Catholic; Gaby Vega , Wilson; Abby Wachter , Notre Dame; Jr. M Haven Snyder , Nazareth; So. Kayla Reed , Palisades; So. Jill Olewine , Northern Lehigh; So. Andie Graney , Freedom; Emily Renner , Northwestern; Abby Dempsey , Faith Christian-Roseto.
